title: Trans Frights holographic sticker
description:
Trans frights are human frights! üëª

Decorate a planner, laptop, notebook or local cis lamppost of your choice with this pulpy trans pun. This holographic variant hits all those 90s Goosebump-book-cover buttons.


CONSTRUCTION 

Designed / drawn by me, printed on high quality holographic sticker stock by StickerApp. According to them, they're pretty much weatherproof for a few years. More information here: https://stickerapp.co.uk/material/holographic-stickers/


DELIVERY

Measures approximately 7cm x 6cm (what I'd call "medium" laptop sticker size), delivered in a card-backed A6 envelope for safety.

Delivery to the UK by Royal Mail First Class and to the EU / US by Royal Mail International Standard.


MORE

There's a plain white variant of this sticker available in the store here: https://www.etsy.com/uk/listing/862705358/trans-frights-vinyl-sticker-halloween
